This paper is about data warehouse design and optimization, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of benchmarks for performance evaluation, which is related to data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper mentions the use of synthetic data generation, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation of the benchmark as a Java software, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL).
